{
  "id": "69d90504e4c152241a4aeaa9",
  "title": "非文芸的サイコソフィア: 二者間の反応モデル",
  "created": 1775830280,
  "updated": 1775832729,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d90504e4c152241a4aeaa9",
      "text": "非文芸的サイコソフィア: 二者間の反応モデル",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3af",
      "text": "from [非文芸的サイコソフィア]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b0",
      "text": "非文芸的サイコソフィア: 二者間の反応モデル",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b1",
      "text": "　経験則をもとにしやすいように、[Nrem.icon]自身のタイプである[VLEF]を例に挙げる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b3",
      "text": "[** [完全なアガペー]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b4",
      "text": "`1P += 4`, `1R > 4`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b5",
      "text": "`2P -= 3`, `2R > 3`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b6",
      "text": "table:完全なアガペー（VLEF–FELV）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b7",
      "text": " \t\t\tF\t\tE\t\tL\t\tV\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b8",
      "text": " \t\t\tPFp\trFr\tpEp\tRER\tpLP\trLR\tPLP\tRLr",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3b9",
      "text": " V\tPVp\trvr\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+\t>",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3ba",
      "text": " L\tplp\tRLR\t\t\t\t\t-\t>\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3bb",
      "text": " E\tpeP\treR\t\t\t+\t<\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3bc",
      "text": " F\tPFP\tRFr\t-\t<\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3be",
      "text": " V",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3bf",
      "text": " 　`1V += 4V (pV)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c0",
      "text": " 　`1V > 4V (Vr)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c1",
      "text": " L",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c2",
      "text": " 　`2L -= 3L (pL)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c3",
      "text": " 　`2L > 3L (LR)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c4",
      "text": " E",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c5",
      "text": "  `3E += 2E ()`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c6",
      "text": "  `3E < 3E (R+)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c7",
      "text": " F",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c8",
      "text": " 　`4F -= 1F (pF)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3c9",
      "text": " 　`4F < 1F (4r)`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3ca",
      "text": " なぜか居心地が良く、自然に対話が発生するが、なぜ引き合うのかがよく分からない関係、と説明される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3cb",
      "text": "　 居心地の良さと理解は別なのかもしれない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3cd",
      "text": "[** #アガペー（サイコソフィア） ([アガペー・フィリア]）]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775831534
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba451",
      "text": "table:アガペー—フィリア（VLEF–VELF）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba452",
      "text": " \t\tV\t\tE\t\tL\t\tF\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba453",
      "text": " \t\tPFp\trFr\tpEp\tRER\tpLP\trLR\tPLP\tRLr",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba454",
      "text": " V\tPVp\t1\t<\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba455",
      "text": " \trvr\t>\t1\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba456",
      "text": " L\tplp\t\t\t\t\t-\t-\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba457",
      "text": " \tRLR\t\t\t\t\t>\t>\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba458",
      "text": " E\tpeP\t\t\t+\t<\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba459",
      "text": " \treR\t\t\t+\t<\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba45a",
      "text": " F\tPFP\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1\t-",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba45b",
      "text": "\t\tRFr\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+\t1",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba45c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba45d",
      "text": "　手続きにおいて、2が3を励起する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba45e",
      "text": "　結果において、2が3を統制する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775830306
    },
    {
      "id": "69d906d90000000000eb632b",
      "text": "　1Vの領域においてお互いをけん制し合うが、目標と利害が一致している場合には問題ではない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830745,
      "updated": 1775830807
    },
    {
      "id": "69d907170000000000eb632c",
      "text": "　　単に相手のいない時に自分の決めたことをするだけ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830807,
      "updated": 1775831584
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9052b0000000000cba461",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830315,
      "updated": 1775830329
    },
    {
      "id": "69d909e00000000000eb6332",
      "text": "このアガペーはモデルTの[協力関係]によく似ている",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775831520,
      "updated": 1775832247
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90b270000000000eb6333",
      "text": "　ならアガペーかつ協力関係のペアは最も都合が良いのではないか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775831847,
      "updated": 1775831939
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9053a0000000000eb6325",
      "text": " 　VELFの代表的な組み合わせはEIEだが、VELFもEIEもEIE-VELFも人口比で稀な類型",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830330,
      "updated": 1775831842
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905800000000000eb6326",
      "text": " 　　LIEに典型的なのはVLEFだが、LIEもVLEFもLIE-VLEFも人口比で極めて稀な類型",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830401,
      "updated": 1775832262
    },
    {
      "id": "69d906800000000000eb632a",
      "text": " 　　そしてEIE-VLEFやLIE-VELFはさらに出現確率の低い組み合わせだろう",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830656,
      "updated": 1775832264
    },
    {
      "id": "69d9064d0000000000eb6328",
      "text": " 　　EIE/LIE-VELFとLIE/EIE-VLEFのペアの発生確率は極めて低いということになる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830605,
      "updated": 1775832158
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905d80000000000eb6327",
      "text": "　　ILE-VLEFのほうが一般的で、遭遇確率も高い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830488,
      "updated": 1775831949
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90b910000000000eb6334",
      "text": "　　　ILE-VLEFとアガペーかつ協力関係になる組み合わせは、理論上はSLE-VLEFだが人間がこの類型に成長するのか怪しい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775831953,
      "updated": 1775832270
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905210000000000cba460",
      "text": "　　では最も日本的なEFVLやFEVLのアガベーのペアならば",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830306,
      "updated": 1775832671
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90d290000000000eb6338",
      "text": "　　　EII/ESI-EFVLやESI/EII-EVLFは一般的だがこれらのアガペーのLII/LSIはいるのかどうか怪しい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775832361,
      "updated": 1775832729
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90e4d0000000000eb6339",
      "text": "　　　",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775832653,
      "updated": 1775832653
    },
    {
      "id": "69d90d1a0000000000eb6336",
      "text": "　　　",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775832346,
      "updated": 1775832347
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3d9",
      "text": "　1V同士の場合、かつお互いの潰瘍を自然に癒してしまう場合、さらに共同作業において目標が一致する場合、",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3da",
      "text": "　　行動を起こす上での合意が形成されるのが早く、ほとんど暗黙のうちに行われる。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3db",
      "text": " 　要するに、行き着くところまで突き進み、暴走しやすい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3dd",
      "text": "[** （フィリア・アガペー）]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3de",
      "text": "table:アガペーB（VLEF–FLEV）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3df",
      "text": " \t\t\tF\t\tL\t\tE\t\tV\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e0",
      "text": " \t\t\tPFp\trFr\tpEp\tRER\tpLP\trLR\tPLP\tRLr",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e1",
      "text": " V\tPVp\trvr\t\t\t\t\t\t\t+\t>",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e2",
      "text": " L\tplp\tRLR\t\t\t\t\t1\t1\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e3",
      "text": " E\tpeP\treR\t\t\t1\t1\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e4",
      "text": " F\tPFP\tRFr\t-\t<\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e6",
      "text": " プロセス部分がまるっきり同じなので表面的には同じように話をするが、4Vが1Vに嫌々付き合わされているみたいになるのだろうか[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775831171
    },
    {
      "id": "69d908180000000000eb632d",
      "text": " 　自動的に協調的な振る舞いになるが、選好の結果として協調しているわけではないような感じ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775831063,
      "updated": 1775831215
    },
    {
      "id": "69d908b80000000000eb632e",
      "text": " 　別に意図して合わせているわけではないが元から同じなので結果的に相手に合わせているみたいになる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775831224,
      "updated": 1775831339
    },
    {
      "id": "69d909340000000000eb632f",
      "text": " 　　そしてそのことをお互いに知っている",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775831348,
      "updated": 1775831384
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e8",
      "text": " 長期的な目標の不一致",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775830280,
      "updated": 1775830280
    },
    {
      "id": "69d905050000000000cba3e9",
